	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hehe, it appears i am a bit late to the discussion, but will put in my 2 cents anyways.<br><br>hmm twinkning a rogue ... <br><br>in the beginning twinkage is all about hp so i would suggest the 2ac 35hp/35mana earring .. electrum black saphire? ... maybe spider fur neck for str, sarnak hide mask ac/str, hmm helm .. dunno is you can wear ssb as a rogue but it has hp, if not go for mrylokars awesome grapic on halflings.&nbsp;&nbsp;ok now to the next row of slots... hmm 6 ac/65 hp rings are a must on all low lvl characters 130 extra hp is thx.  for wrists i would go with SC bracers, hp/str/ac/blahblah uber droppable bracers, gloves, CC 20 ac and 10 str is thx, arms CC again hehe i love that stuff ac/str/sta.  shoulders hmm maybe imbured granite spaulders /shrug i wear an obulus mantle (gimp but oh well) belt spider fur or TBB, spider fur has hp / str TBB has well 15 str, legs... maybe peerless dragonhide nice ac with dex and agi, boots CC prolly cuz nice ac / str and some other stats.  for weapons i would suggest maybe cbol or seb dirk main, and maybe the other offhand unless of course you wanna keep up other skills so maybe a guard captains mallet for 1hb or edge of the nightwalker for 1hs ... hehe almost forgot bp and cloak ... easy enough .. fungi and CoF or CoCW .. maybe get shimmering terror hide cloak and get a CCoM .. hmm blah blah ramble ramble<br><br>would be an awesome twink ... only cost around 250 - 300kpp<br>&nbsp;<br>~Tactikal Mizkalculation~&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>60 ASSASSIN <br>Cruxor Thunderblade<br>Level 51 gimp Paladin<br>Vazaelle<br></td></tr>
